   - Unboundedly many agent identities X with fresh long-term keys Ksx, registered privately (insert).
   - Publicly output identities (not keys) so peers can reference each other.
   - Replicated Initiator/Responder/RevealHelper per identity.
   - Replicated stateless Server using the global registration store.
